    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sheet material in which the medium is made from cardboard with a honeycomb core. Acid-free honeycomb board is used  in conservation as a support panel in treatment of materials and objects such as parchment, textiles, maps, and drawings. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
